## Chapter 5 — Demonstration

The prototype successfully demonstrated:

- Vehicle detection and counting in outdoor test conditions
- ESP8266 receiving motor commands over Wi-Fi from a mobile app
- Bidirectional divider movement controlled by L298N motor driver
- Real-time annotated images showing bounding boxes around detected vehicles
- Lane decision logic (high traffic → expand lane, low traffic → reduce lane width)

